race.comment: BONCAPO (12) is a colt by Street Boss on debut for the Ciaron Maher yard. His trials have just been fair but he draws the inside and has to be respected for the yard. SARAYA (10) is going well in search of that elusive win and draws for every chance. She won't need to improve much to be going close. DURHAM (13) resumes. From a proven family which includes Group 2 winner Old North. All nine of his siblings to have raced have won. Maiden prep was underwhelming however may have just needed time to mature. HEART'S EMBRACE (7) is a full sister to city placegetter Miss Dynamo. Readied for this with two trials at Coleraine and Murtoa.
